### Get all patients
GET http://localhost:3001/api/patients

### Create a new patient with valid data
POST http://localhost:3001/api/patients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "dateOfBirth": "1985-06-15",
  "ssn": "123-45-6789",
  "gender": "male",
  "occupation": "Software Engineer"
}

